{"tid":1602572,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"台灣人與香港同行，我哋雙十都要同台灣慶祝國慶","createTime":"2019-09-29T12:37:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T13:03:36.000Z","uid":243854,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"85b620dc8414027007c74ad4253abd9407bb721e","tid":1602572,"uid":243854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T12:37:24.000Z","msg":"同全世界講，中華民國(台灣)先係正統中國<br />\n117周年，你支那共匪先70周年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以前我會覺得台灣攬住中華民國先係一大問題，如果以台灣名義喺國際上獨立反而少阻滯<br />\n不過既然中共咁鍾意玩中華情義，咁就同佢玩中華民國，睇你班支那狗點樣講人賣國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b7df6bdfe17816fa45d459251092bf9dcf6377e","tid":1602572,"uid":243854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T12:39:47.000Z","msg":"支那都係認孫中山為國父<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁國父建立嘅中華民國喺邊呢"},{"pid":"26c85077671c6b6cf50745cb387d4e575d4e1616","tid":1602572,"uid":146285,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T12:41:07.000Z","msg":"正確黎講係108年<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中華民國的國慶日，又稱雙十節、雙十國慶、雙十慶典、武昌起義紀念日、辛亥革命紀念日等，定於1911年武昌起義的發動日10月10日。"},{"pid":"06bc7176510c5179f1013ffbcec538cd685c5cb4","tid":1602572,"uid":303982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T12:41:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"708ed2e85b03da1fe9b737d097f7f3889c61d728","tid":1602572,"uid":303982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T12:41:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1e6ee98610f9f3db67a070f17d2888bf7110e539","tid":1602572,"uid":243854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26c85077671c6b6cf50745cb387d4e575d4e1616","tid":1602572,"uid":146285,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T12:41:07.000Z","msg":"正確黎講係108年<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中華民國的國慶日，又稱雙十節、雙十國慶、雙十慶典、武昌起義紀念日、辛亥革命紀念日等，定於1911年武昌起義的發動日10月10日。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T12:43:33.000Z","msg":"係，但我見佢12年先計建國，所以唔識點計佢好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34644c1d09e9e7a8debc20154affa38949e4df1d","tid":1602572,"uid":123440,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T12:43:58.000Z","msg":"好忙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9321c887e2216152e277b5b92e7bdebf8e956c81","tid":1602572,"uid":270506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T12:44:49.000Z","msg":"【十月行動討論】抵制十一，歡慶雙十，全民贈慶！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1581858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1581858</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4439a9906c62df7324138465b9c2d16daa941cde","tid":1602572,"uid":243854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34644c1d09e9e7a8debc20154affa38949e4df1d","tid":1602572,"uid":123440,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T12:43:58.000Z","msg":"好忙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T12:52:52.000Z","msg":"推下先，推到文宣JJ入嚟，等下無人行<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcf6ecb3db9a1e5c7f4937227c164c1e342e398b","tid":1602572,"uid":63669,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T12:55:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />小陣，人地依家想同中國劃清界線你就衝埋去話人地係中國，你係咪high大左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31e03921199b14488bbf84526e63ee60b50e7cd2","tid":1602572,"uid":263349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T12:56:36.000Z","msg":"台灣唔係個個都 想過雙十架 <br />\n<br />\n台灣人想獨立 唔係中華民國獨立 <br />\n<br />\n係建台灣國 去民國呀"},{"pid":"6e72b3aa6ae217f66747ac2179f4df4a9063fa0a","tid":1602572,"uid":243854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bcf6ecb3db9a1e5c7f4937227c164c1e342e398b","tid":1602572,"uid":63669,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"cit